1
00:00:00,270 --> 00:00:02,040
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,110 --> 00:00:03,240
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,310 --> 00:00:05,210
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:07,480 --> 00:00:08,750
(Episode 78)

5
00:00:09,650 --> 00:00:10,820
Who killed whom?

6
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:12,880
And what do you mean
you lived as your sister?

7
00:00:13,790 --> 00:00:15,850
What's all of this about?

8
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:33,370
The bloodstain doesn't match
Oh Jung Ran's?

9
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:38,510
So, you're saying
Oh Jung Ran isn't the killer?

10
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:41,110
It wasn't Driver Song either.

11
00:00:44,950 --> 00:00:47,120
This must be a huge shock
for President Kim.

12
00:00:49,050 --> 00:00:52,420
She must feel like her last 30 years
have crumbled.

13
00:00:54,630 --> 00:00:57,460
But we can't jump
to conclusions yet.

14
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:00,430
It's possible Oh Jung Ran found out
and tampered with it.

15
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:05,000
First, please check the lab
that ran the test.

16
00:01:09,210 --> 00:01:11,180
Are you saying...

17
00:01:12,740 --> 00:01:14,680
you're not my mother?

18
00:01:15,810 --> 00:01:17,720
My real mother was murdered,

19
00:01:19,450 --> 00:01:20,920
and because you're her twin,

20
00:01:21,550 --> 00:01:24,220
you took her identity
and spent 30 years seeking revenge?

21
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:25,660
Min Jun.

22
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:30,230
How could you live as someone else
for 30 years?

23
00:01:32,230 --> 00:01:33,500
Back then,

24
00:01:34,730 --> 00:01:36,330
I had no other choice.

25
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:41,070
I desperately wanted
to clear my sister's name,

26
00:01:42,470 --> 00:01:45,540
and I wanted to protect you
after you'd lost your mother.

27
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,610
You should've told me sooner.

28
00:01:48,810 --> 00:01:50,780
I was worried about
how much it would hurt you,

29
00:01:52,850 --> 00:01:55,750
and I couldn't let you
get consumed by revenge too.

30
00:01:58,890 --> 00:01:59,890
Luckily,

31
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:04,330
I met Jin Ju
and got the evidence I needed,

32
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:08,030
and I was about
to tell you everything.

33
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:12,200
I'm sorry you had to find out...

34
00:02:13,810 --> 00:02:14,810
this way.

35
00:02:15,670 --> 00:02:18,140
You got the evidence from Jin Ju?

36
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:21,180
What do you mean by that?

37
00:02:22,010 --> 00:02:23,180
Dr. Baek.

38
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:27,190
Jin Ju's late father and I...

39
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,750
had a history.

40
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:38,760
What are you doing here
without calling?

41
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:41,070
I missed you.

42
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:45,040
I wanted to have dinner together...

43
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:46,800
and talk about something.

44
00:02:47,970 --> 00:02:50,040
Come in. Have a seat.

45
00:02:57,050 --> 00:02:58,050
(DNA Analysis Report)

46
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,720
What's that?

47
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:06,490
- What?
- Am I not supposed to see it?

48
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:08,560
It seemed like you were hiding it.

49
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,300
It's nothing like that.

50
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,640
You said you had
something to discuss.

51
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,100
What is it?

52
00:03:22,740 --> 00:03:25,280
What are you up to
with President Kim?

53
00:03:26,950 --> 00:03:29,150
- What?
- I saw the two of you together...

54
00:03:29,650 --> 00:03:31,380
in front of the house yesterday.

55
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:33,150
Since when did you two get so close?

56
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:35,090
Are those documents
you're hiding from me...

57
00:03:35,490 --> 00:03:37,060
related to her?

58
00:03:41,690 --> 00:03:46,660
I'll tell you later.
I can't talk about it right now.

59
00:03:47,230 --> 00:03:50,030
Is there something
you can't tell me?

60
00:03:50,940 --> 00:03:52,200
When you...

61
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:56,140
keep secrets and lie about things,
am I just supposed to say nothing?

62
00:03:56,210 --> 00:03:58,040
What exactly am I to you?

63
00:04:04,850 --> 00:04:06,520
This isn't why I came here.

64
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,490
I wanted to talk to you...

65
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,290
about registering our marriage.

66
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,100
We'll talk about this
some other time.

67
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,990
I always thought it was strange...

68
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:48,160
that Jin Ju and I
have the same birthday.

69
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:50,560
But we were actually...

70
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:55,400
born on the same day,
in the exact same place.

71
00:04:56,570 --> 00:04:58,170
Jin Ju's father...

72
00:04:58,870 --> 00:05:01,410
even saved my life,

73
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:05,180
and the man
who brutally murdered him...

74
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:08,080
was my own father.

75
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:19,160
Why did my mother fall
for a man like him?

76
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:23,260
Because she was deceived
by Park Tae Ho's lies.

77
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:25,900
Myung Hui...

78
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:29,100
believed Park Tae Ho
when he told her he was a widower.

79
00:05:29,930 --> 00:05:32,100
She truly wanted to build
a family with him.

80
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,570
When she found out...

81
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:38,240
that Park Tae Ho
was already married,

82
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:41,850
your mother...

83
00:05:43,050 --> 00:05:46,080
actually tried to leave him,
even while carrying you.

84
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:51,360
My birth mother...

85
00:05:51,790 --> 00:05:53,560
What was she like?

86
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:57,900
Since you were twins,

87
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:05,000
you must've looked
exactly alike, right?

88
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:10,710
My mother...

89
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:15,480
I want to meet her.

90
00:06:28,830 --> 00:06:31,830
(The late Kim Dan Hui)

91
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:49,880
(The late Kim Dan Hui,
Oct 14, 1973 - Oct 7, 1997)

92
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:52,750
Myung Hui.

93
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:56,720
Min Jun's here.

94
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:02,260
You must've missed him so much.

95
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:07,030
I'm sorry it took so long.

96
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,940
Min Jun,

97
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,110
this is your mother.

98
00:07:18,210 --> 00:07:19,440
Say hello.

99
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,350
So...

100
00:07:30,990 --> 00:07:33,560
this is where my mother really is?

101
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:37,360
You...

102
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:43,370
look so much like her.

103
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:49,240
I'm begging you, Dan Hui.

104
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,840
Please, live for me.

105
00:07:58,220 --> 00:08:00,220
I need that strength
to protect my child too.

106
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:02,150
Help me do that, Dan Hui.

107
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:04,320
Your mother...

108
00:08:04,690 --> 00:08:07,090
was a warm and strong person.

109
00:08:07,930 --> 00:08:11,330
She didn't give up on me
when I was dying.

110
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:13,330
She saved me.

111
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,800
(The late Kim Dan Hui,
Oct 14, 1973 - Oct 7, 1997)

112
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:18,000
She was the same way with you.

113
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:23,210
Even in that tragic situation,

114
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:27,140
she loved you with all her heart.

115
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,480
And even as she was dying,

116
00:08:38,660 --> 00:08:40,730
she didn't give up on you.

117
00:08:41,490 --> 00:08:43,690
Myung Hui, please.

118
00:08:49,970 --> 00:08:51,100
The baby's alive.

119
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:53,440
She made sure...

120
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,940
The baby's alive.

121
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:56,240
you survived.

122
00:08:57,380 --> 00:09:00,280
Your mother saved me,

123
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,450
and you.

124
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:05,080
She protected and saved us both.

125
00:09:26,940 --> 00:09:28,170
I guess that's why...

126
00:09:30,410 --> 00:09:32,540
I wanted to protect you too.

127
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:48,430
Of all the things
Myung Hui left behind,

128
00:09:48,730 --> 00:09:50,330
this is her last letter.

129
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,230
Now...

130
00:09:56,530 --> 00:09:59,140
I think it's right
for you to have it.

131
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:27,770
It pains me to do this,

132
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:30,770
but I have to get away from him.

133
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:34,240
I can't let my child
live in this nightmare.

134
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:41,810
Mom...

135
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,350
Mom...

136
00:10:57,830 --> 00:10:59,060
Yoon Jung.

137
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:02,000
It's okay.

138
00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:04,340
Myung Hui...

139
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:06,470
She'd be happy.

140
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:11,110
The little boy who lost his mother
right after he was born...

141
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:13,510
grew up to be so wonderful...

142
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,750
and upstanding.

143
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,090
She'd be overjoyed.

144
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:40,940
Thank you.

145
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:46,480
All I can really say to you...

146
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:49,610
is just that.

147
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,550
All this time,

148
00:11:54,090 --> 00:11:56,950
I never realized
how much I was loved.

149
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:01,330
I finally understand now.

150
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,010
Don't worry.

151
00:12:22,250 --> 00:12:23,550
From now on,

152
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,380
I'll be the one...

153
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:30,390
to protect everyone.

154
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:43,430
(The late Kim Dan Hui)

155
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,190
Mother.

156
00:13:15,430 --> 00:13:18,800
To me, you'll always be my mother.

157
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,710
I came to see my birth mother,

158
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:28,180
but here I am, seeing you again.

159
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:33,780
It took me too long to realize...

160
00:13:34,390 --> 00:13:37,320
that you risked your whole life
to protect me.

161
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:41,260
Carrying that heavy burden
all by yourself,

162
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:44,300
you must've been lonely for so long.

163
00:13:52,170 --> 00:13:55,470
I'll share your burden...

164
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:58,640
and be by your side.

165
00:14:02,110 --> 00:14:03,110
All right.

166
00:14:05,650 --> 00:14:06,850
Min Jun.

167
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:09,690
My son.

168
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:36,550
I'm so proud of Min Jun,
aren't you too?

169
00:14:37,050 --> 00:14:39,920
He must be more shocked
and devastated than anyone,

170
00:14:41,090 --> 00:14:42,720
but he worried about me first,

171
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:45,560
and accepted...

172
00:14:47,020 --> 00:14:48,360
me...

173
00:14:48,990 --> 00:14:50,460
as his mother.

174
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:55,900
But I...

175
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:59,540
don't even know
who killed Myung Hui.

176
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:02,540
If it wasn't Oh Jung Ran...

177
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:05,540
Then for the past 30 years,

178
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:09,050
what have I been doing?

179
00:15:11,350 --> 00:15:13,280
You raised Min Jun.

180
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:18,420
He's warm like Myung Hui,
and resilient like you, Dan Hui.

181
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:22,860
Even if Oh Jung Ran
isn't the killer,

182
00:15:23,330 --> 00:15:26,460
it's a fact
that she went after little Min Jun.

183
00:15:26,730 --> 00:15:29,130
And you said she used poison.

184
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:32,140
If that drug put Myung Hui
in more danger,

185
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:37,170
then Oh Jung Ran
isn't entirely innocent.

186
00:15:37,910 --> 00:15:40,040
So don't blame yourself.

187
00:15:40,410 --> 00:15:42,180
We just have to find
the real killer.

188
00:15:43,210 --> 00:15:46,550
Someone other than Oh Jung Ran...

189
00:15:48,090 --> 00:15:50,020
A killer
we didn't even know existed.

190
00:15:50,950 --> 00:15:52,420
A different killer?

191
00:15:59,830 --> 00:16:02,130
What are you talking about?

192
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:04,270
Her memory came back?

193
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:06,840
Yes, Kim Myung Hui made a scene...

194
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:08,970
after claiming
her memories were back.

195
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:11,340
It's a joke though.

196
00:16:11,810 --> 00:16:16,080
Nothing she says is right.
She's accusing me of strangling her.

197
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:17,380
What?

198
00:16:18,850 --> 00:16:19,850
Strangling her?

199
00:16:19,850 --> 00:16:23,290
Exactly, and it's ridiculous.

200
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:27,420
I think the shock of being kicked out
made her snap.

201
00:16:27,490 --> 00:16:28,930
She's out of her mind.

202
00:16:28,930 --> 00:16:32,130
Before she completely loses it,
lock her up in a mental hospital.

203
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:34,030
Kim Myung Hui...

204
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:37,230
Her memory is back?

205
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:38,970
It's not her memory.

206
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:41,000
I'm telling you,
she's lost her mind.

207
00:16:52,980 --> 00:16:56,520
Hold on.
Why are you in such a bad mood?

208
00:16:58,720 --> 00:17:01,490
Because nobody does what I want.

209
00:17:01,990 --> 00:17:04,060
Even after being offered
the successor position,

210
00:17:04,130 --> 00:17:06,630
Hyun Jun insists
he'll never break up with Chloe.

211
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:08,830
And even when I tell Park Tae Ho
that Kim Myung Hui is crazy,

212
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:11,300
he refuses to kick her out
and just keeps her around.

213
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:15,040
I'm so frustrated I could scream.

214
00:17:15,610 --> 00:17:18,110
In that case,
let me give you a hand.

215
00:17:18,810 --> 00:17:23,550
I think I can make Hyun Jun
and Chloe break up.

216
00:17:24,820 --> 00:17:27,020
You think you can do
what Park Tae Ho and I couldn't?

217
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,790
How?

218
00:17:29,790 --> 00:17:32,760
Just make Hyun Jun
be the one to give up.

219
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:37,260
Don't tell me you're going
to blackmail him with his secret.

220
00:17:37,530 --> 00:17:40,960
Go after my son,
and I'll destroy you first.

221
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:44,800
No, not that.
I have a far more interesting plan.

222
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:48,940
We can play a little game
using Park Min Jun and Chloe.

223
00:17:49,140 --> 00:17:53,110
Make it look like
Chloe betrayed Hyun Jun.

224
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:54,850
A betrayal?

225
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:59,320
The sting of betrayal is only
as deep as the love...

226
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:01,450
you once felt.

227
00:18:02,450 --> 00:18:04,860
I'll give it a try.
Is that okay with you?

228
00:18:04,990 --> 00:18:06,060
(Bit Life President, Oh Jung Ran)

229
00:18:06,060 --> 00:18:09,460
Fine. Give it a shot.

230
00:18:09,930 --> 00:18:12,730
Good thinking. I'll see to it...

231
00:18:12,730 --> 00:18:15,670
that Hyun Jun and Chloe break up.

232
00:18:20,670 --> 00:18:23,810
So, Min Jun found out everything?

233
00:18:23,870 --> 00:18:27,080
Yes. He and Dan Hui
visited the columbarium...

234
00:18:27,140 --> 00:18:28,910
to pay their respects to Myung Hui,

235
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:31,420
and we all broke down in tears
for a long time.

236
00:18:32,450 --> 00:18:36,320
Wow, everyone must be
in complete shock.

237
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:40,360
Ms. Kim must be shocked
that Oh Jung Ran isn't the killer,

238
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:41,860
and Mr. Park...

239
00:18:43,090 --> 00:18:44,960
must be devastated by the news
about his birth mother.

240
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:48,800
Wait, so are you sure
Oh Jung Ran isn't the killer?

241
00:18:48,970 --> 00:18:52,170
Yes, I double-checked with the lab.

242
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:53,940
The results showed no signs
of tampering.

243
00:18:53,940 --> 00:18:56,440
Then who in the world could it be?

244
00:18:56,670 --> 00:18:57,670
I have...

245
00:18:58,310 --> 00:19:00,540
someone in mind.

246
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:02,780
Who do you think it was?

247
00:19:04,820 --> 00:19:06,480
Chairman Park Tae Ho.

248
00:19:09,050 --> 00:19:10,290
Chairman Park?

249
00:19:10,290 --> 00:19:13,690
No way. How could he do that
to the woman...

250
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:15,030
who's carrying his child?

251
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:19,930
Hold on.
Yoon Jung, are you with her on this?

252
00:19:20,130 --> 00:19:22,170
Honestly, if it wasn't Oh Jung Ran,

253
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:24,900
he's the next most likely suspect.

254
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:28,610
Wait. Then what does that mean
for Dan Hui's life?

255
00:19:29,110 --> 00:19:32,410
This is even more shocking
than learning it wasn't Oh Jung Ran.

256
00:19:32,410 --> 00:19:36,350
Dan Hui's life would be
completely ruined, beyond repair.

257
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:40,450
That's why we have to find out
for sure, right now.

258
00:19:40,550 --> 00:19:42,890
We need to make things right
as soon as possible.

259
00:19:45,320 --> 00:19:47,360
I hope it wasn't him either.

260
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:52,160
For Dan Hui and Min Jun's sake,
I'm praying it wasn't Park Tae Ho,

261
00:19:52,860 --> 00:19:54,870
of all people.

262
00:19:55,630 --> 00:20:00,170
But we can't just overlook
our prime suspect.

263
00:20:00,170 --> 00:20:01,170
You're right.

264
00:20:01,970 --> 00:20:03,810
Secretary Jung is right.

265
00:20:05,180 --> 00:20:08,250
No matter how hard it is,
we have to set things right.

266
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:09,950
That's what we do for friends.

267
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:12,850
Then let's re-run the test...

268
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:16,190
and see if it matches
Chairman Park's DNA.

269
00:20:16,490 --> 00:20:19,160
Yes, let's do that.

270
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:29,300
Ms. Chloe, what brings you here?

271
00:20:29,370 --> 00:20:31,870
I left a lot of my things behind.

272
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,440
I came to pack some
of Ms. Kim's things...

273
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,070
and take them to the annex.

274
00:20:37,640 --> 00:20:40,740
Sure. Go right ahead.

275
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:41,750
Right.

276
00:20:44,980 --> 00:20:46,920
By the way, Mrs. Ok,

277
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:51,360
I'd like to take some fruit
and drinks to the annex.

278
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:52,690
Fruit and drinks?

279
00:20:52,690 --> 00:20:56,090
Yes. Ms. Kim
hasn't been eating lately,

280
00:20:56,090 --> 00:20:57,790
and I'm really worried.

281
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:02,100
- Could you help me out?
- Of course.

282
00:21:14,810 --> 00:21:17,380
This should work for the DNA test.

283
00:21:35,970 --> 00:21:38,870
Why are you here?

284
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:41,510
I came to pick up my things.

285
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:46,080
I'll be on my way now.

286
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:57,690
(Choi Yu Na, the Design Thief!)

287
00:21:57,690 --> 00:22:00,290
I'm going to plaster these
all over the company walls.

288
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:04,730
It's not enough to make up
for breaking my Hyun Jun's heart,

289
00:22:05,130 --> 00:22:09,170
but at least she won't be able
to show her face at the office.

290
00:22:10,530 --> 00:22:11,540
Excuse me.

291
00:22:11,970 --> 00:22:13,000
What?

292
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:20,340
Hey, why are you taking these down?
They weren't easy to put up.

293
00:22:20,410 --> 00:22:22,180
These are unauthorized posts.

294
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:25,380
This is in the public interest.

295
00:22:25,450 --> 00:22:28,220
It's exposing the wrongdoing
of Team Leader Choi Yu Na.

296
00:22:28,290 --> 00:22:29,790
Even so, you can't just post them
wherever you want.

297
00:22:30,090 --> 00:22:31,090
Please leave.

298
00:22:31,150 --> 00:22:35,430
No, wait. Hey, let go of me!

299
00:22:36,730 --> 00:22:37,730
Hyun Jun...

300
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,100
Hold on.

301
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,470
Aren't you Ms. Oh Jung Ran's driver?

302
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:51,880
Drivers belong
in the basement waiting room.

303
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:54,280
Don't just wander around
and get in the way.

304
00:22:55,380 --> 00:22:56,850
Just a second.

305
00:22:58,350 --> 00:22:59,520
Yes, Director?

306
00:23:05,060 --> 00:23:06,120
Let him go.

307
00:23:06,920 --> 00:23:07,920
What?

308
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:13,560
I said, let him go
and be on his way.

309
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:17,100
- But, sir...
- Do I need to repeat myself?

310
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:19,140
No, sir.

311
00:23:26,480 --> 00:23:27,710
Hyun Jun.

312
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:49,130
Sorry to bother you.

313
00:23:49,830 --> 00:23:50,830
It's fine.

314
00:23:51,570 --> 00:23:53,740
Here are the test results.

315
00:23:54,910 --> 00:23:55,970
Thanks.

316
00:23:59,410 --> 00:24:00,410
(DNA Analysis Report)

317
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:01,580
(The DNA from the bloodstain...)

318
00:24:01,580 --> 00:24:03,950
(does not match either
Oh Jung Ran or Song Geun Tae.)

319
00:24:07,550 --> 00:24:09,750
You probably already heard
from your mother,

320
00:24:10,790 --> 00:24:12,160
but it wasn't Oh Jung Ran.

321
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:14,660
Right.

322
00:24:15,430 --> 00:24:17,330
Still, I wanted to see for myself.

323
00:24:18,460 --> 00:24:21,900
This isn't just my mother's fight
anymore. It's mine now.

324
00:24:23,470 --> 00:24:26,970
I have to find the person
who murdered my birth mother...

325
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:29,170
thirty years ago.

326
00:24:31,370 --> 00:24:35,750
Thank you for opening the P.O. box
and helping my mother.

327
00:24:37,580 --> 00:24:41,220
It's something I had to do,
for my dad's sake.

328
00:24:44,690 --> 00:24:47,020
This must be so confusing for you.

329
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:52,230
All I can say is that...

330
00:24:53,130 --> 00:24:54,130
I'm sorry.

331
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,300
I'm just now realizing...

332
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:02,070
how much you must have suffered.

333
00:25:05,580 --> 00:25:08,910
I don't even remember my mother,
and I don't know who the killer is,

334
00:25:10,010 --> 00:25:12,580
but just the fact that her life
was wrongfully taken...

335
00:25:14,450 --> 00:25:15,750
is suffocating.

336
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:19,420
But you...

337
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:22,160
lost the father you loved
in such a way.

338
00:25:24,930 --> 00:25:26,900
And on top of that, the person
who murdered your father...

339
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,470
is my father.

340
00:25:32,370 --> 00:25:35,240
If the blood on the pearl
matches Chairman Park's,

341
00:25:36,540 --> 00:25:38,440
that means the person
who killed your mother...

342
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:41,110
is none other than your father.

343
00:25:46,580 --> 00:25:50,090
Things might get even harder
for you.

344
00:25:51,620 --> 00:25:53,760
But I hope you get through it.

345
00:25:55,230 --> 00:25:56,930
For your mother's sake, at least.

346
00:25:57,660 --> 00:26:02,030
Right. I'll find the killer
and protect my mother.

347
00:26:37,500 --> 00:26:40,800
(Head of Division 2, Park Hyun Jun)

348
00:26:45,910 --> 00:26:46,910
Baek Jin Ju.

349
00:26:48,210 --> 00:26:50,350
We left things like that,
and you didn't even call me once?

350
00:26:52,150 --> 00:26:53,580
At times like this,
all I want to do...

351
00:26:55,090 --> 00:26:56,790
is pick up the phone
and talk to you.

352
00:26:58,390 --> 00:26:59,620
Is that too much to ask?

353
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:03,260
Park Hyun Jun.

354
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:11,840
Just leave, will you?

355
00:27:13,100 --> 00:27:14,470
I will after showing you this.

356
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:18,040
It's a photo
you absolutely have to see.

357
00:27:29,250 --> 00:27:32,490
It looked like those two
were meeting in secret.

358
00:27:33,090 --> 00:27:34,090
What's going on?

359
00:27:34,990 --> 00:27:36,060
Did you know about this?

360
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:42,330
Park Min Jun and Chloe.

361
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:44,470
Don't you think
the feelings are mutual?

362
00:27:49,510 --> 00:27:51,780
I don't care
if you mess around with my secret.

363
00:27:54,810 --> 00:27:56,850
But if you're using Chloe
to play games,

364
00:27:58,080 --> 00:27:59,520
I'll never forgive you.

365
00:28:01,020 --> 00:28:02,720
Do you like Chloe that much?

366
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:09,330
Don't trust her too much.
You'll only end up getting hurt.

367
00:28:10,330 --> 00:28:12,360
Never forget
how I gave my heart to Min Jun,

368
00:28:14,930 --> 00:28:16,430
only to end up brokenhearted.

369
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:22,970
You and I are different.

370
00:28:23,510 --> 00:28:25,340
Stop spouting nonsense and get out.

371
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:28,080
Fine. I'm leaving.

372
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:55,240
A different killer?

373
00:28:56,670 --> 00:28:57,970
A different killer...

374
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:02,680
Back then, 30 years ago,

375
00:29:03,910 --> 00:29:06,380
if it wasn't Oh Jung Ran
or Song Geun Tae,

376
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:08,550
then Park Tae Ho...

377
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:14,560
No. It can't be.

378
00:29:15,290 --> 00:29:16,830
Even a monster
wouldn't do that to her...

379
00:29:17,990 --> 00:29:20,460
while she was pregnant
with his child.

380
00:29:20,830 --> 00:29:21,930
There's just no way.

381
00:29:26,300 --> 00:29:30,470
I planted a bug in the annex
to keep an eye on Oh Jung Ran.

382
00:29:37,050 --> 00:29:38,050
It's me.

383
00:29:39,120 --> 00:29:40,620
I need a favor.

384
00:29:41,450 --> 00:29:44,520
Jin Ju, that listening device
you put in the annex living room...

385
00:29:45,050 --> 00:29:46,290
Can I use it for a little while?

386
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:48,160
The listening device?

387
00:29:48,890 --> 00:29:50,290
If it isn't Oh Jung Ran,

388
00:29:50,290 --> 00:29:53,060
that leaves Park Tae Ho.
I need to confirm it.

389
00:29:54,730 --> 00:29:55,800
I hid the bug...

390
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:58,230
inside the dog ornament
on the living room shelf.

391
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,400
Also...

392
00:30:01,670 --> 00:30:04,570
I'm at the lab now, waiting.

393
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:10,750
I'm here to see if the blood
matches Chairman Park.

394
00:30:10,880 --> 00:30:12,480
You suspect Park Tae Ho, too?

395
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:14,380
Just being thorough.

396
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:17,050
I'll call you
the second the results come out.

397
00:30:18,090 --> 00:30:19,390
Okay, got it.

398
00:31:01,360 --> 00:31:02,500
What are you doing here?

399
00:31:02,930 --> 00:31:05,270
I have something to tell you, sir.

400
00:31:05,840 --> 00:31:08,540
You've been waiting for me without
even knowing when I'd be back?

401
00:31:08,970 --> 00:31:11,640
I dropped by because it's around
the time you normally get off work.

402
00:31:16,650 --> 00:31:17,650
So,

403
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:20,050
what did you want to talk about?

404
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:23,450
I wanted to ask about
what happened 30 years ago.

405
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:27,690
What happened 30 years ago?

406
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:31,290
I remembered something
from back then,

407
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:35,670
but I'm not sure
if it's a real memory.

408
00:31:37,100 --> 00:31:38,330
What did you remember?

409
00:31:39,140 --> 00:31:40,700
Someone tried to kill me.

410
00:31:41,370 --> 00:31:43,010
They were choking me.

411
00:31:43,510 --> 00:31:45,740
Other than Oh Jung Ran,
was there anyone else...

412
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:48,750
who wanted me dead 30 years ago?

413
00:31:55,180 --> 00:32:00,220
(A: DNA Test Consultation,
B: Sample Collection, C: Results)

414
00:32:04,460 --> 00:32:05,800
Here are the results.

415
00:32:06,400 --> 00:32:07,430
Right, thank you.

416
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,210
(DNA Analysis Report)

417
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:17,840
(The DNA from the bloodstain...)

418
00:32:17,910 --> 00:32:19,710
(doesn't match Park Tae Ho.)

419
00:32:21,610 --> 00:32:22,810
They don't match?

420
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:27,620
Then it wasn't Park Tae Ho either?

421
00:32:49,470 --> 00:32:52,480
(Pearl in Red)

422
00:32:52,580 --> 00:32:54,810
Your incredible devotion to Chloe...

423
00:32:55,180 --> 00:32:57,180
I wonder how long it'll last.

424
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:58,750
It's bound to fall apart anyway,

425
00:32:59,080 --> 00:33:00,220
so don't try so hard.

426
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:04,890
I'll be the one you drag along
for your greed over the Adele Group.

427
00:33:04,890 --> 00:33:08,490
Just please let Mother go
so she can start a new life.

428
00:33:08,560 --> 00:33:10,260
I can't stomach living
as a mistress,

429
00:33:10,260 --> 00:33:12,260
and watching her become
the chairman's wife is even worse.

430
00:33:12,430 --> 00:33:14,260
I'll do it.
I'll officially marry you.

431
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:16,100
Kim Myung Hui, hey!

432
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:18,800
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
